heading: Maulwood Dungeon Guide
content: Maulwood is an incredible dungeon featuring the highly valuable , a critical Codex of Power aspect for Barbarian Leveling. It has a quick and easy completion time and simple objectives. Stock up on your Sigils for this one; you'll run it over and over again for massive hordes of loot! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
